-- PRESS DIGEST - Portugal - Nov 17
-- 
-- Mon Nov 17, 2014 03:35AM EST
-- None



LISBON, Nov 17 (Reuters) - Following are some of the main stories in Portuguese newspapers on Monday. Reuters has not verified these stories and does not vouch for their accuracy.

* Resignation of interior minister forces Prime Minister Pedro Passos Coelho to consider reshuffle (Publico) * Interior minister resigns in "golden visa" scandal, ruling party wants to purge secrete services (Diario de Noticias) * Bank of Portugal Gov. Costa to be heard as parliament starts inquiry into Banco Espirito Santo (Negocios) * Siphoning of cash to offshore firms paid some Grupo Espirito Santo debts (Economico)